252
00:17:15,647 --> 00:17:17,774
Silakan pergi jika sudah selesai.

253
00:17:19,818 --> 00:17:22,988
Tidak dengar ucapanku? Mau kuantar keluar?

254
00:17:24,322 --> 00:17:27,284
Aku muak kecewa padamu.

255
00:17:27,743 --> 00:17:28,994
Jadi, mohon enyahlah.

