00:19:24,276 --> 00:19:25,986
- Halo?
- Ya, makanlah sekarang.

290
00:19:26,486 --> 00:19:27,654
Astaga.

291
00:19:28,113 --> 00:19:30,031
Bukan daging sapi untuk makan malam tim?

292
00:19:30,657 --> 00:19:32,784
Kita bekerja di Choong, bukan Song & Kim.

293
00:19:33,493 --> 00:19:35,745
- Makanlah.
- Benar. Rekaman CCTV-nya?

294
00:19:36,413 --> 00:19:38,290
Detektif yang bertugas mengambilnya.

295
00:19:38,832 --> 00:19:41,001
Detektif Lee? Namun,
