Bu Boo.

299
00:19:51,344 --> 00:19:52,512
Kalian baik-baik saja?

300
00:19:53,221 --> 00:19:54,472
Senang bertemu denganmu.

301
00:19:54,556 --> 00:19:56,600
- Kau akan bergabung dengan kami?
- Ya.

302
00:19:56,683 --> 00:19:57,642
Duduklah.

303
00:19:57,726 --> 00:19:59,019
- Duduklah.
- Duduklah.

304
00:19:59,644 --> 00:20:02,355
- Beri dia sendok dan sumpit.
- Ini.

305
00:20:02,439 --> 00:20:04,065
- Kau merekrut Bu Boo?
- Ya.

306
00:20:04,357 --> 00:20:06,109
Dia akan menangani kasus ayahmu.

307
00:20:06,568 --> 00:20:08,820
Yang lain terlalu sibuk
dengan kasus Ha Chan-ho.

308
00:20:10,238 --> 00:20:12,365
Ada apa?

309
00:20:12,657 --> 00:20:13,742
Kau tak keberatan?

310
00:20:14,367 --> 00:20:15,368
Tak apa.

311
00:20:15,785 --> 00:20:17,662
- Kenapa tidak?
- Makanlah ini.

312
00:20:17,746 --> 00:20:19,664
- Bu Boo, dia penyidik kita.
- Sumpitmu.

313
00:20:19,748 --> 00:20:21,458
- Ini menyenangkan.
- Astaga.

314
00:20:21,541 --> 00:20:23,126
Makan malam tim macam apa ini?

315
00:20:23,376 --> 00:20:25,211
Bu, bisa pesan 12 botol soju?

316
00:20:25,295 --> 00:20:26,254
Ini dia.

317
00:20:31,760 --> 00:20:34,596
Choong!

318
00:20:36,181 --> 00:20:37,015
Terima kasih.

319
00:20:37,599 --> 00:20:38,642
Tidak, jangan.

320
00:20:38,725 --> 00:20:40,894
- Mari minum. Bersulang.
- Minum air saja.

321
00:20:40,977 --> 00:20:42,103
- Bersulang.
- Bersulang.

322
00:20:45,941 --> 00:20:47,192
Jangan!

323
00:20:53,198 --> 00:20:54,783
- Dia sudah menelannya.
- Ada apa?

324
00:20:54,866 --> 00:20:56,034
Waktu kita satu menit.

325
00:20:58,244 --> 00:20:59,204
"Satu menit"?

326
00:20:59,287 --> 00:21:00,705
- Lihat saja nanti.
- Astaga.

327
00:21:14,260 --> 00:21:15,762
Ini akan dimulai.

328
